In recent years India's demand for electricity has soared as its economy has grown.

But it faces problems as its power infrastructure struggles to keep up with its growing needs.

Analyst predict that unless there is a huge investment in the energy sector, the country will see many more power failures which could jeopardise its future as as a superpower.

